text: Akchishma () is a rural locality (a village) in Khalikeyevsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 41 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 17 km from Sterlibashevo, 8 km from Khalikeyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Akchishma
